OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening, with some late sunshine.
OL,7,
OL,8,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for many, but
OL,9,Fsimilar to Monday, this cloud will
OL,10,Fburn away through the morning to leave
OL,11,Fanother largely sunny day. Very warm
OL,12,For hot again in places.
OL,13,
OL,14,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,15,FLargely dry through this period, with
OL,16,Fcloud developing overnight, burning
OL,17,Faway by day to give sunny spells.
OL,18,FStaying very warm or hot, especially
OL,19,Finland, but cooler along northeastern
OL,20,Fcoasts.
